<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mirabeer | Premium Brews</title>

    <!-- Google Font -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0e0e0e;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        header {
            padding: 30px 50px;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 80px 50px;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .card {
            background: #161616;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #222;
        }

        .card h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .card p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #ccc;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    MIRABEER
</header>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Premium Beer Selection</h1>
    <p>Crafted for those who value quality, taste, and experience. Explore a curated collection of premium brews.</p>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>Our Collection</h2>
        <p>Classic Lager</p>
        <p>Strong Ale</p>
        <p>Premium Stout</p>
    </div>

    <a href="#" class="btn">Order Now</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
